Version:          1.0.1
Release:          3%{?dist}%{?buildtag}
Summary:          Bounded Density Estimation

License:          GPL-2
URL:              https://cran.r-project.org/package=%{packname}
Source0:          %{url}&version=%{packver}#/%{packname}_%{packver}.tar.gz


BuildRequires:    R-devel >= 2.0
Requires:         R-core >= 2.0
BuildArch:        noarch
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-shiny 
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-ggplot2 
BuildRequires:    R-methods 
Requires:         R-CRAN-shiny 
Requires:         R-CRAN-ggplot2 
Requires:         R-methods 

%description
A collection of S4 classes which implements different methods to estimate
and deal with densities in bounded domains. That is, densities defined
within the interval [lower.limit, upper.limit], where lower.limit and
upper.limit are values that can be set by the user.

